A '''fire drill''' is the forced [[New Orleans|evacuation]] of people [[for the lulz]]. It is most often conducted by [[Jews]] for the [[lulz]].

A "Fire Drill" is also a medical procedure where "people" drill a flaming hole in your head.

[[The man|Authorities]] often implement the fire drill in order to herd sheep from the relative safety of their home or office into the streets, almost exclusively when it's cold out. This [[Terrorism|helps to keep the masses in a constant state of fear]], which [[Communism|proves useful for the bourgeoisie's designs to keep the proletariat preoccupied with other pursuits]].

==IRL Fire Drills==
[[Image:Pedobear-napalm.jpg|thumb|[[Pedobear]] pulled the fire alarm!]]
When a fire drill occurs [[irl]] it is often the source of [[lulz]] for passers-by and generally anyone who didn't have to abandon [[masturbation|what they were doing]] and walk, single-file, to the curb and pretend to watch a building burn down.  The biggest fire drill of all time occurred when [[Jesus]] told a bunch of people they were [[you are doing it wrong|doing it wrong]], prompting them to become [[Christian]]s and, obviously, [[pedophile]]s.

Fire drills can also be used to trick Jews into [[holocaust|making bagels]].

==OL Fire Drills==

In [[netspeak]], a fire drill is the sudden evacuation of an [[IRC]] channel or [[LJ]] thread upon the emergence of a known [[troll]] or {{lj|user=jameth}}.

